room_title: Escape room "Elude The Illusionist" by Hour To Exit in New York
room_description:
The Great Zoltar is a famous stage magician, entertaining large audiences nearly every night. You and your friends are also magicians - and concerned citizens. Lately, it seems like all of the competition has been mysteriously disappearing!
You know it has something to do with Zoltar because every time a magician drops out, he takes their spot in the limelight. What is happening to the other magicians? You only have one hour to sneak into Zoltarâ€™s dressing room and find out!
